    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cloaks or long coats of a distinctive type worn by soldiers or horsemen in the 16th-17th centuries; examples are coats worn by musketeers and gardes du corps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
